sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Claude as Claude Code
    participant Health as v0_healthcheck
    participant Context as prepare_prototype_context
    participant Proto as generate_prototype
    participant Handoff as handoff_to_claude_dev
    participant V0 as v0 API

    Note over User,V0: Prototype Workflow (4 Steps)

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,Health: Optional: Verify API
        User->>Claude: Check API status
        Claude->>Health: v0_healthcheck()
        Health->>V0: Test connection
        V0-->>Health: API status
        Health-->>Claude: ✅ Connection OK
        Claude-->>User: API verified
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over User,Context: Step 1: Parse Requirements
        User->>Claude: "Build TaskMaster with dashboard, task list, settings"
        Claude->>Context: prepare_prototype_context(description, images?)
        Context->>Context: Parse screens, platform, goals
        Context-->>Claude: ✅ Context prepared<br/>(product, platform, screens)
        Claude-->>User: Show parsed context
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over User,Proto: Step 2: Generate Prototype
        User->>Claude: Generate prototype
        Claude->>Proto: generate_prototype(context, model, streaming)
        Proto->>V0: POST /prototype with screens

        loop For each screen
            V0-->>Proto: Stream progress
            Proto-->>Claude: Update progress
            Claude-->>User: Screen N/M generated
        end

        V0-->>Proto: Complete prototype
        Proto-->>Claude: ✅ Prototype done<br/>(screens, components, preview)
        Claude-->>User: Show preview link
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 245)
        Note over User,Handoff: Step 3: Implementation Brief
        User->>Claude: Create implementation brief
        Claude->>Handoff: handoff_to_claude_dev(prototype_id, result, context)
        Handoff->>Handoff: Extract UX patterns<br/>Component list<br/>Implementation rules
        Handoff-->>Claude: ✅ Brief created<br/>(patterns, rules, components)
        Claude-->>User: Show implementation brief
    end

    Note over User,V0: Ready for Implementation by Claude Dev
